android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.WRITE_SECURE_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the system's secure settings data. Not for use by common applications.

android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to perform operations like adding and removing accounts and deleting their password.

playstore_details.title: YouCam Makeup-Magic Selfie Cam & Virtual Makeovers
playstore_details.description:
Beautify your selfies in seconds with YouCam Makeup, the leading AR makeup & selfie camera app. Try makeup looks from hundreds of beauty brand products with our live makeup cam - you can even record a makeup video right on the app!

Edit selfies and touch up your photos with face makeover, hair color, lipstick, skin tone, teeth whitening, skin smoother, eyebrows, eye color, contour, makeover styles and more! 

YouCam Makeup Core Features
❤ Live makeup cam - try out real cosmetic products from top beauty brands instantly.
❤ AR makeovers in real-time, including lipstick, lip art, eyeliner, eye color, lashes, and more! 
❤ Hair makeover & hair color, including single color or ombré hair!
❤ Edit selfies with beautiful selfie filters, instant face shaper, 3D accessories, jewelry, hats, sunglasses & more.
❤ Airbrush face tune - face editing with face smoother & blemish editor.
❤ AI detect skincare cam for analysis & tracking.
❤ Receive the latest makeup tips and tutorials from the beauty community for social sharing.

【YouCam Makeup Premium Version 】
◇ Upgrade to YouCam Makeup Premium for unlimited access to:
◇ Exclusive makeup collections
◇ Lip art styles and Lip Reshaper
◇ Beautifying tools including one-tap Eye Tuner, Concealer & Face Shaper and Nose Enhancer
◇ Save photos in HD
◇ Teeth Whitener tool gives you the brightest smile
◇ Remove watermarks
◇ Single color & ombre hair editor
◇ An AD-FREE editing experience
◇ Monthly NEW premium content delivered to you
◇ Select any makeover style you like for any occasion and instantly show off your perfect look anytime anywhere!

【Top Beauty Brands to Try Before You Buy】
★ AR beauty products in all the latest makeup colors and styles.
★ Try makeup with exclusive looks and more with realistic AR brand products before you shop

【Hair Makeover, Hair Color & Hairstyle in One Tap】
★ Hair coloring in 360 degrees - dye your hair like Billie Eilish or however you want!
★ Hair dying and more from a real-time salon experience
★ Hairstyle choices and haircuts range from long hair, short hairstyles, curly hair or straight

【Flawless Skin & Face Editor】
★ Selfie editor complete with foundation, lipstick, contour, eye makeup & blush 
★ Face editor with skin smoother & skin tone whether you want flawless skin or freckles
★ Concealer to remove dark circles, eye bags and shine for a flawless, natural look

【Analyze Skin Health】
★ Keep your skin healthy and radiant with our new skincare analysis and Skin Diary 
★ Skincare analyses analyzes the health of your skin in seconds
★ Wrinkles, spots, acne and dark circles can be analyzed instantly with relative scores

【Lips】
★ Lipstick and lip gloss in classic matte color or high shine colors.
★ Lip Enhancements & Gleaming Teeth; get a natural, confident smile every time
★ Try out lip colors from major beauty brands & many more

【Eyes & Brows】
★ Get magic eye color shine with smart tools to conceal under eye circles & remove red eyes.
★ Mascara tool instantly adds volume & length to lashes.
★ Change eye color and overlay makeup to style your look up or down.
★ Eyebrow editor - easily find the best eyebrow style for your face

【Top Trending Celebrity Makeup Looks】
★ Try makeovers from the hottest celebrities and more glam looks 
★ Red carpet makeup looks from Hollywood stars and social influencer makeup styles

【Special Makeup Looks】
★ Princess makeup looks featuring Cinderella, Ariel (the Little Mermaid), Belle and Jasmine
★ Find one-of-a-kind horoscope looks for Aquarius, Pisces, Aries, Taurus, Gemini, Scorpio, and all the rest

【3D Accessories - Add a Touch of Style】
★ Get a realistic new look with 3D accessories including hats, hairbands & more.
★ Like a virtual shopping trip to the mall! 

Get more beauty inspo: https://www.instagram.com/youcamapps/
More details, visit us at http://www.perfectcorp.com/consumer/apps/ymk
Bugs? Please contact us at YouCamMakeup_android@perfectcorp.com
